This work was packaged for Debian by:

    OTB Team <contact@orfeo-toolbox.org> on Wed, 09 Apr 2014 15:44:20 +0200

It was downloaded from <http://hg.orfeo-toolbox.org/>, using command:

    hg clone -r <version> http://hg.orfeo-toolbox.org/OTB

The source tarball is an aggregate of several different works in which the
main one, developed by the CNES (Centre National d'Etudes Spatiales), is
Orfeo-Toolbox (OTB).


Internal dependencies (included third-party works):

* ITK (http://www.itk.org/),
  distributed under the Apache 2.0 license
  (see Copyright/ITKCopyright.txt or
       http://www.itk.org/ITK/project/license.html)

* VTK (http://www.vtk.org/),
  distributed under the revised BSD license
  (see Copyright/VTKCopyright.txt or
       http://www.vtk.org/Wiki/VTK/License)

* VXL (http://vxl.sourceforge.net/),
  distributed under a specific license (simplified BSD-like)
  (see Copyright/VXLCopyright.txt or
       http://sourceforge.net/p/vxl/git/ci/master/tree/core/vxl_copyright.h)

* OSSIM (http://www.ossim.org/),
  distributed under the GNU LGPL 2.1 license
  (see Copyright/OSSIMCopyright.txt or /usr/share/common-licenses/LGPL-2.1)

* LibSVM (http://www.csie.ntu.edu.tw/~cjlin/libsvm/),
  distributed under the revised BSD license
  (see Copyright/LibSVMCopyright.txt or
       https://github.com/cjlin1/libsvm/blob/master/COPYRIGHT)

* OpenJPEG (http://www.openjpeg.org/),
  distributed under the revised BSD license
  (see Copyright/OpenJPEGCopyright.txt or
       http://www.openjpeg.org/BSDlicense.txt)

* OpenThreads (http://www.openscenegraph.org/),
  distributed under the OpenSceneGraph Public License (OSGPL) 0.0, i.e.
  wxWindows Library License
  (see Copyright/OpenThreadsCopyright.txt)

* SiftFast (http://libsift.sourceforge.net/),
  distributed under the GNU LGPL 3.0 license
  (see Utilities/otbsiftfast/LICENSE or /usr/share/common-licenses/LGPL-3)

* ConfigFile (http://www-personal.umich.edu/~wagnerr/ConfigFile.html),
  distributed under the MIT license
  (see Copyright/ConfigFileCopyright.txt)

* Insight Journal Publications (http://www.insight-journal.org/browse/publications),
  distributed under the revised BSD license
  (see Copyright/ITKCopyright.txt or
       http://www.itk.org/ITK/project/license.html)

* ISO C9x compliant inttypes.h and stdint.h for Microsoft Visual Studio
  Utilities/otbmsinttypes/inttypes.h
  Utilities/otbmsinttypes/stdint.h
  distributed under the revised BSD license
  (see header of above files)

* 6S (http://6s.ltdri.org/)
  No license information available on the website but the authors gave CNES
  the permission to use 6S code inside OTB and to release it under CeCILL v2
  license. FIXME: add a link to the authorization.


External dependencies (not included third-party works):

* GDAL (http://www.gdal.org/),
  distributed under the X/MIT license

